email_content:
Hello,

I hope this email finds you well in these unprecedented times.

I am reaching out because I came across your company and thought it might be interesting to connect. My cousin mentioned something about shipping but I'm not entirely sure if that's what you do.

I have a friend who might be interested in some business opportunities in the logistics sector. Are you interested in partnership opportunities? Or maybe investment?

Also, I noticed your website has some information but I couldn't find the section about the thing I was looking for. Do you have more details about your services? I'm not sure exactly what I need but maybe you can help.

Please advise on next steps.

Thank you and have a blessed day.
